    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "As the Body of Christ, we would all let Him grow,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "From our spirit expand, from our heart overflow;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Thus, we’ll build up the church and make ready the Bride;"
            }
          ]
