          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Lord, in these days rekindle our love toward You.”"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "chorus"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Now the world stage is set and the Lord’s coming soon."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "He’ll be not first the Judge, but our lovely Bridegroom."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "As we follow the Lamb, He is mingled with us."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "When He sees we’ve been prepared, He’ll come to marry us."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
